340
00:24:09,520 --> 00:24:13,120
我不知道 他曾经为工会走私亚力酒 就这样
I don't know. He was smuggling arak for the unions. That's it.

341
00:24:13,240 --> 00:24:14,640
别这样 你知道康
Oh, come on. You know Kang.

342
00:24:14,800 --> 00:24:16,400
他就会投机取巧 不过不是激进分子
He's an opportunist, but he's not an activist.

343
00:24:16,520 --> 00:24:18,520
他不会走私炸药的
He's not going to smuggle C-4.

344
00:24:18,680 --> 00:24:20,320
- 你现在找到什么吗? - 还没有
- Have you found anything yet? - Not yet.

345
00:24:20,480 --> 00:24:21,848
好吧 你们根本找不到 
Well, you're not going to.  

346
00:24:21,849 --> 00:24:22,720
我们会继续搜查
We'll keep searching.

347
00:24:22,880 --> 00:24:24,560
我们要扣押你的船 直到康被审判
And... we're impounding your boat until Kang's trial.

348
00:24:24,680 --> 00:24:26,040
等一下 等一下
Oh, hang on, hang on.

349
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:29,120
你甚至没有考虑过康可能是被陷害的吗?
You're not even going to consider the possibility that Kang was set up?

350
00:24:29,240 --> 00:24:31,200
如果你错了 他要被吊死
If you're wrong, he'll hang.

351
00:24:31,320 --> 00:24:33,560
我来告诉你我考虑的是什么
I'll tell you what I'll consider.

352
00:24:33,680 --> 00:24:35,040
带林杰志来见我
Bring me Lim Chee Kit,

353
00:24:35,200 --> 00:24:36,960
我可能会把你朋友往积极的方面想
I may take a favourable view towards your friend.

354
00:24:37,120 --> 00:24:39,240
你认为齐基特计划了爆炸事件?
You think Chee Kit planted the explosives?

355
00:24:39,400 --> 00:24:43,480
我不知道 但你把他带来的时候我会考虑
I don't know, but I'll consider that when you bring him to me.

356
00:24:46,400 --> 00:24:48,440
为什么 所以你要带他去见警察?
Why, so you can take him to the police?

357
00:24:48,600 --> 00:24:49,920
不 我只是想和他说话  
No, I just want to talk to him.

358
00:24:49,921 --> 00:24:51,240
你认为他是无辜的 是吗?
You think he's guilty, don't you?

359
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:53,840
我不知道 我想找到谁该对爆炸事件负责
I don't know. I want to find out who's responsible for the bombing.

360
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:56,240
- 我说了 不是林教授 - 你又不知道
- I told you. It's not Professor Lim. - But you don't know that.

361
00:24:56,360 --> 00:24:57,720
但我知道如果找不到谁在他船上藏了爆炸物
But I know Kang will hang

362
00:24:57,880 --> 00:24:59,920
康会被吊死
if we can't find out who planted explosive on his boat.

363
00:25:00,040 --> 00:25:01,400
你想看他被吊死吗?
Do you want to see him hang?

364
00:25:01,520 --> 00:25:03,800
对不起 我无能为力
Sorry. There's nothing I can do.

365
00:26:23,120 --> 00:26:25,440
- 不许动 - 你想干什么?
- Don't move. - What do you want from me?

366
00:26:25,600 --> 00:26:27,560
- 你是谁? - 你不会想知道的
- Who are you? - You don't want to know.

367
00:26:27,720 --> 00:26:29,400
我没做错任何事情 
I've done nothing wrong. 

368
00:26:29,401 --> 00:26:31,640
不许动 这不对 费利克斯
Don't move. That's not true, Felix.

369
00:26:32,640 --> 00:26:34,760
别看我
Don't look at me.

370
00:26:36,680 --> 00:26:38,400
这是你的签名吗?
Is that your signature?

371
00:26:38,560 --> 00:26:40,520
- 你从哪得到的? - 这是你的签名吗?
- Where did you get it from? - Is that your signature?

372
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:42,440
是
Yes.

373
00:26:42,560 --> 00:26:44,960
现在 你指控陈苏...
Now, you accused Ch'en Su...

374
00:26:45,080 --> 00:26:46,600
别看我!
Don't look at me!

375
00:26:46,760 --> 00:26:50,000
你指控 陈苏玲是共产党的支持者
You accused Ch'en Su Ling of being a communist sympathiser.

376
00:26:50,160 --> 00:26:51,600
- 是真的吗? - 不!
- Is that true? - No!

377
00:26:51,720 --> 00:26:53,320
那你为什么要撒谎 费利克斯?
Then why did you lie, Felix?

378
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:54,960
我很生气
I was angry.

379
00:26:55,080 --> 00:26:57,240
我的父母...
My parents...

380
00:26:57,400 --> 00:27:00,560
...他们以为我们会很合适
..they thought that we'd be a good match together,

381
00:27:00,720 --> 00:27:04,000
但是她对我没有兴趣
but she just wasn't interested in me.

382
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:07,800
所以你做了一个假报告 是吗? 是不是?
So you made a false report, did you? Did you?

383
00:27:07,960 --> 00:27:08,761
我会撤回那个 
I'll retract it. 

384
00:27:08,762 --> 00:27:10,480
我会告诉他们我撒谎了闭嘴 闭嘴
I'll tell them I lied. Shut up, shut up.

385
00:27:10,640 --> 00:27:13,000
接下来 你什么也不要说
This is what you're going to do. You're going to say nothing.

386
00:27:13,160 --> 00:27:15,280
如果有任何人问起你那上面有什么
If anyone ever asks you what was in that,

387
00:27:15,440 --> 00:27:18,680
你就否认你交过它 明白了吗?
you're going to deny you ever gave it, is that understood?

388
00:27:18,800 --> 00:27:20,560
是的 我什么也不说
Yes. I will say anything.

389
00:27:20,720 --> 00:27:23,480
如果我再听到你说陈苏玲任何消息
If I ever hear of you giving information on Ch'en Su Ling again

390
00:27:23,640 --> 00:27:27,360
我会再来这 我知道你住在哪
I will come back here. I know where you live.

391
00:27:27,520 --> 00:27:29,360
现在 站起来 面向墙 别看着我
Now, get up, face the wall. Don't look at me.

392
00:27:29,480 --> 00:27:31,720
别看我 面向墙
Don't look at me. Face the wall.

393
00:27:31,840 --> 00:27:33,720
数到五十
Count to 50.

394
00:27:33,840 --> 00:27:35,200
好的
OK.

395
00:28:11,040 --> 00:28:15,040
肯定是工会的人指使的阿拉克
It must have been one of the union guys that ordered the arak.

396
00:28:15,200 --> 00:28:17,720
在找到你之前就已经装好了
It would have been loaded in before it got to you.

397
00:28:17,840 --> 00:28:19,800
我猜是的
Yeah, I guess.

398
00:28:19,960 --> 00:28:23,400
但是我说了 我认不出来他们
But I told you  I can't identify any of them.

399
00:28:23,520 --> 00:28:26,560
我们要找出齐基特
We've got to find Chee Kit.

400
00:28:26,680 --> 00:28:30,080
也许他知道些什么
Maybe he knows something.

401
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:32,640
如果是齐基特干的呢?
What if it WAS Chee Kit?

402
00:28:32,760 --> 00:28:35,240
我会把他带来
I'll bring him in.

403
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:40,200
投弹手就交给你了 这是和阿姆兰的交易
The bomber for you. That was the deal with Amran.

404
00:28:40,320 --> 00:28:43,560
你知道我上哪能找到他吗?
Do you know where I can find him?

405
00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:45,400
康?
Kang?

406
00:28:45,520 --> 00:28:48,000
我不知道他住在哪...
I don't know where he lives...

407
00:28:49,000 --> 00:28:51,640
...但我知道他在哪祷告
...but I do know where he prays.

408
00:31:07,640 --> 00:31:10,120
别再跟踪我了 任务结束了
Stop tailing me. The job's finished.

409
00:31:10,280 --> 00:31:12,640
你的兄弟不相信你不是我们的错
It's not our fault your brother doesn't trust you.

410
00:31:12,800 --> 00:31:17,240
他知道你和阿姆兰探员之间的交易吗?
Does he know about your deal with Inspector Amran?

411
00:31:17,400 --> 00:31:20,640
我在警察局有很多人脉
I have many sources in the police department,

412
00:31:20,800 --> 00:31:22,920
我会毫不犹豫的利用他们
and I wouldn't hesitate to use them

413
00:31:23,040 --> 00:31:25,440
来保护我哥哥
to protect my brother.

414
00:31:32,440 --> 00:31:33,440
不好意思

415
00:33:51,240 --> 00:33:52,920
新加坡的大街上已经有
Already there's too much violence

416
00:33:53,040 --> 00:33:54,560
太多暴力事件了
on the streets of Singapore.

417
00:33:54,720 --> 00:33:56,680
我们的组织对这些事没有采取任何措施
Our union has never resorted to such things.

418
00:33:56,680 --> 00:33:58,480
时代在改变

419
00:33:58,680 --> 00:34:00,980
我们不应该继续被外国人欺压

420
00:34:00,980 --> 00:34:03,480
这件事是应该被表扬的

421
00:34:03,480 --> 00:34:06,480
- 是我吩咐的 - 你应该!

422
00:34:07,480 --> 00:34:09,480
我们的人民已经厌倦了等待！

423
00:34:09,480 --> 00:34:11,480
那是一次错误

424
00:34:11,480 --> 00:34:13,080
唯一的错误是

425
00:34:13,480 --> 00:34:14,980
炸药不够

426
00:34:15,480 --> 00:34:17,880
我们的目标应该是内阁会议

427
00:34:18,240 --> 00:34:20,920
不! 如果我们杀掉政府官员
No! If we kill government officials,

428
00:34:21,080 --> 00:34:23,560
那么就不会再有人支持我们了
there will be no support among the people.

429
00:34:23,720 --> 00:34:26,280
- 那就把他们都干掉 - 不!
- Then we'll take them all out. - No!

430
00:34:26,400 --> 00:34:28,200
每个炸弹都会让英国人
Every bomb is another excuse

431
00:34:28,360 --> 00:34:31,240
有理由把军队留下来
for the British to leave their troops here.

432
00:34:31,400 --> 00:34:34,080
只要我还是工会的领头人
While I am the leader of this union,

433
00:34:34,200 --> 00:34:35,800
我们就不能使用暴力
we will not use violence.

434
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:37,800
警察 举手站起来!

435
00:34:46,520 --> 00:34:48,000
不! 不能用枪
No! No guns.

436
00:34:48,120 --> 00:34:50,120
不能用枪!
No guns!

437
00:35:24,120 --> 00:35:25,520
如果你不想死

438
00:35:25,820 --> 00:35:26,720
跟我来

439
00:35:28,040 --> 00:35:30,640
- 你是谁? - 苏玲的朋友
- Who are you? - A friend of Su Ling's.

440
00:35:32,240 --> 00:35:34,400
你别无选择
You've got no choice.

441
00:35:47,320 --> 00:35:49,360
这边
This way.

442
00:36:16,800 --> 00:36:19,560
你为什么要帮我?
Why are you helping me?

443
00:36:19,720 --> 00:36:21,360
我不想和我哥哥有任何关系
I don't want anything to do with my brother.

444
00:36:21,520 --> 00:36:23,244
我不为你哥哥工作 
I don't work for your brother. 

445
00:36:23,245 --> 00:36:25,440
我这么做是为了小康 - 康?
I'm doing this for Xiao Kang. - Kang?

446
00:36:25,600 --> 00:36:28,040
他是我的朋友 他被陷害了 现在在监狱
He's a friend of mine. He's in prison for something he didn't do.

447
00:36:28,160 --> 00:36:31,040
警察为什么抓他?
What do the police think he did?

448
00:36:31,200 --> 00:36:33,760
他们认为他为你们工会走私炸药
They think he smuggled explosives for your union.

449
00:36:35,520 --> 00:36:37,800
他们是对的
They're right.

450
00:36:37,920 --> 00:36:39,720
等等 等等!
Wait. Wait!

451
00:36:39,880 --> 00:36:42,400
我说了 等下! 你说什么 康做了什么?
I said, wait! What are you talking about, what did Kang do?

452
00:36:42,520 --> 00:36:43,880
你想听实话?
You want the truth?

453
00:36:44,040 --> 00:36:46,120
康为高和那些好战分子走私炸药
Kang smuggled weapons for Gao and the militant ones.

454
00:36:46,240 --> 00:36:47,600
不 不 不 不 他没有
No. No, no. No, he didn't.

455
00:36:47,760 --> 00:36:49,840
但他和邮局的事没有关系
But he had nothing to do with the post office.

456
00:36:49,960 --> 00:36:51,400
那都是高义做的
That was all Gao Yi.

457
00:36:51,520 --> 00:36:54,400
我劝过他 但是...
I tried to get him to stop but...

458
00:37:16,600 --> 00:37:18,600
救我
Help me.

459
00:37:22,200 --> 00:37:24,600
坚持下 叫救护车!
Hang in there. Get an ambulance!

460
00:37:24,720 --> 00:37:26,440
快点 叫救护车!
Quickly, get an ambulance!

461
00:37:33,680 --> 00:37:36,760
齐基特没有命令袭击邮局
Chee Kit didn't order the attack on the post office.

462
00:37:36,880 --> 00:37:38,600
谁命令的?
Who did?

463
00:37:38,720 --> 00:37:40,200
他说应该是高义
He said it could have been Gao Yi.

464
00:37:40,320 --> 00:37:43,040
你看到是谁开枪打的他吗?
Did you see who shot him?

465
00:37:43,200 --> 00:37:45,600
嘿 山姆... 我有个主意
Hey, Sam... I've got an idea.

466
00:37:50,040 --> 00:37:53,240
叔叔? 如果我想找个医生来取出子弹
Uncle? If I was looking for a doctor to take out a bullet,

467
00:37:53,400 --> 00:37:55,960
不能问问题 我该去哪?
no questions asked, where would I go?

468
00:37:55,960 --> 00:37:57,060
不能找医生啊

469
00:37:57,060 --> 00:37:58,060
为什么?

470
00:37:58,360 --> 00:37:59,960
他们会报警

471
00:38:01,060 --> 00:38:02,960
我带你去找后门的医生

472
00:38:30,080 --> 00:38:31,760
见到这个很惊讶吗?
Surprised to see that?

473
00:38:31,880 --> 00:38:34,320
我不知道这是什么
I don't know what it is.

474
00:38:34,480 --> 00:38:36,280
这需要点说服力 但是那个后门医生
It took some persuading, but that backstreet doctor

475
00:38:36,440 --> 00:38:38,600
已经承认是他从彭立的肩膀取出这颗子弹的
admitted that he pulled it out of Peng Li's shoulder.

476
00:38:38,760 --> 00:38:40,400
- 彭立 我的手下? - 是的
- Peng Li who works for me? - That's right.

477
00:38:40,560 --> 00:38:42,680
他今晚没来上班
He didn't show up to work tonight.

478
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:45,120
我想知道发生了什么事
I wondered what had happened.

479
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:51,120
你哥哥可能要死了
Your brother is probably going to die.

480
00:38:51,280 --> 00:38:56,240
他能告诉警察什么 让你这么害怕?
What is it you're so scared that he could possibly tell the police?

481
00:38:57,640 --> 00:39:00,320
我听说你当时在那
I heard you were there.

482
00:39:00,480 --> 00:39:03,720
在我哥哥中枪之前他说什么了吗?
Did my brother say anything before you let him get shot?

483
00:39:03,880 --> 00:39:07,200
总有一天你会后悔这么说的
You're going to regret saying that one day.

484
00:39:07,360 --> 00:39:09,240
你不会想成为我的敌人的 卡拉汉先生
You don't want me to be an enemy, Mr Callaghan.

485
00:39:09,360 --> 00:39:11,120
现在说这个有点晚了
It's a bit late for that.

486
00:39:13,040 --> 00:39:15,320
如果你的人跟踪警察...
If your man followed the cops...

487
00:39:17,440 --> 00:39:20,880
...他们怎么知道我在哪的?
...how the hell did they know where I was?

488
00:39:50,520 --> 00:39:53,000
交易就是交易 对吧?
A deal's a deal, huh?

489
00:39:53,160 --> 00:39:55,720
他们抓到投弹手然后放我走了
They caught the bomber and they let me go.

490
00:39:55,840 --> 00:39:57,880
我欠你个人情 伙计 谢谢
I owe you one, man. Thanks.

491
00:39:58,880 --> 00:40:02,880
那么... 齐基特还能活命吗?
So is... Chee Kit going to live?

492
00:40:03,040 --> 00:40:07,000
你还关心这个? 是你告诉警察他在哪的
What do you care? You told the police where he was.

493
00:40:10,160 --> 00:40:13,080
你为什么不等等? 我会把他活着弄出来的
Why didn't you wait? I would have got him out alive.

494
00:40:13,240 --> 00:40:15,720
我别无选择 伙计 他们已经知道...
I didn't have a choice, man. They already knew...

495
00:40:15,840 --> 00:40:18,240
你一直都有选择
You've always got a choice.

496
00:40:18,400 --> 00:40:22,960
警察欠你的 康 他们欠你的!
The police own you, Kang. They own you!

497
00:40:23,120 --> 00:40:27,360
听着 我当初就告诉你了 不是我没说
Look, I told you about this first. It's not like I didn't tell you.

498
00:40:27,520 --> 00:40:29,160
至少和你在这 我觉得 你知道
At least with you there, I thought, you know,

499
00:40:29,320 --> 00:40:31,360
齐基特还有机会出来
Chee Kit could have a chance that he could get out.

500
00:40:31,520 --> 00:40:33,560
我知道他和邮局的事无关
I knew he had nothing to do with the post office.

501
00:40:33,720 --> 00:40:35,163
为什么我要相信你? 
Why should I believe you? 

502
00:40:35,164 --> 00:40:37,040
你陷害我 你欺骗我工会的事
You set me up, you lied about the unions,

503
00:40:37,200 --> 00:40:39,960
欺骗我走私的事 欺骗我关于齐基特的事
you lied about the smuggling, you lied about Chee Kit.

504
00:40:40,120 --> 00:40:42,160
- 你陷害我 康! - 他们要杀了我!
- You set me up, Kang! - They were going to hang me!

505
00:40:50,680 --> 00:40:53,320
我早就知道你是在装无辜
I always knew you'd play an angle.

506
00:40:54,840 --> 00:40:58,080
这对我来说没什么
I didn't have a problem with that.

507
00:40:58,240 --> 00:41:01,640
但我从来... 从来没想到你会这样欺骗我
But I never... I never thought you'd lie to me like that.

508
00:41:09,200 --> 00:41:11,400
他可能就要死了
He's probably going to die.

509
00:41:13,760 --> 00:41:16,040
我们结束了
We're done.

510
00:41:20,440 --> 00:41:22,960
我们早就结束了 山姆
We've been done for a while, Sam.

511
00:41:38,080 --> 00:41:40,840
你好啊 亲爱的
Hello, darling.

512
00:41:40,960 --> 00:41:44,360
你看起来 跟平常一样漂亮
You look beautiful, as usual.

513
00:41:44,480 --> 00:41:46,240
我们可以走了吗?
Shall we?

514
00:41:46,360 --> 00:41:48,280
我... 我觉得我们该回去
I... I think we should go.

515
00:41:49,480 --> 00:41:52,240
听着 对不起 克莱尔
Look, I'm so sorry, Claire.

516
00:41:52,400 --> 00:41:55,240
我知道 过去这六个月 我几乎每周末都出差
I know, these last six months, I've been gone nearly every weekend.

517
00:41:55,400 --> 00:41:58,200
- 弗兰克... - 不 请你让我说完
- Frank... - No, let me finish, please.

518
00:41:58,320 --> 00:42:00,080
我跟麦斯威尔谈过了
I've spoken to Maxwell.

519
00:42:00,240 --> 00:42:03,080
他也同意我一直在干着三个人的活儿
He agrees I've been doing the job of three men.

520
00:42:03,240 --> 00:42:05,228
所以 他会给我请个助手 
So, he's getting me an assistant 

521
00:42:05,229 --> 00:42:06,720
还给我一个周的假期
and giving me a two-week vacation

522
00:42:06,840 --> 00:42:08,680
从今晚开始
starting tonight.

523
00:42:08,840 --> 00:42:11,724
你想去哪里我们就去哪里... 
We can go anywhere you want...

524
00:42:11,725 --> 00:42:13,840
意大利 澳大利亚 美国
Italy, Australia, the US.

525
00:42:14,280 --> 00:42:15,920
随便说
You name it.

526
00:42:16,040 --> 00:42:17,760
我哪里也不想去
I don't want to go anywhere.

527
00:42:17,920 --> 00:42:20,360
那我们就待在这儿 放松一下 睡个懒觉
Then we can stay here. Relax, sleep late.

528
00:42:20,520 --> 00:42:23,760
- 随便你想干什么 - 弗兰克...
- Whatever you want to do. - Frank...

529
00:42:23,920 --> 00:42:26,480
...我真的觉得我们该回家
...I really think we should go home.

530
00:42:26,600 --> 00:42:27,960
怎么了?
What's wrong?

531
00:42:29,880 --> 00:42:32,920
听着 我不想在这里说 我觉得我们该回家
Look, I don't want to do this here. I think we should go home.

532
00:42:33,040 --> 00:42:35,400
说什么? 怎么了?
Do what here? What is it?

533
00:42:35,520 --> 00:42:37,840
克莱尔?
Claire?

534
00:42:38,000 --> 00:42:41,040
弗兰克 我喜欢上了别人 我要搬走了
Frank, I've met someone. I'm moving out.

535
00:42:53,600 --> 00:42:55,320
谁?
Who?

536
00:42:55,440 --> 00:42:57,120
弗兰克...
Frank...

537
00:42:57,280 --> 00:42:58,680
- 是谁? - 嘘!
- Who is it? - Shh!

538
00:42:58,800 --> 00:43:01,000
我想喊就喊
I'll shout if I want to.

539
00:43:02,000 --> 00:43:03,480
是谁 克莱尔?
Who is it, Claire?

540
00:43:04,600 --> 00:43:06,080
山姆・卡拉汉
Sam Callaghan.

541
00:43:12,400 --> 00:43:17,120
- 你开玩笑吧 - 我不是有意这样的
- You're kidding me. - I didn't plan on any of this.

542
00:43:17,240 --> 00:43:19,320
你喜欢他多久了?
How long have you been seeing him?

543
00:43:19,480 --> 00:43:21,400
- 弗兰克 - 多久?
- Frank. - How long?

544
00:43:23,680 --> 00:43:25,200
有几个月了
A couple of months.

545
00:43:29,680 --> 00:43:33,520
这么说你要搬去跟山姆・卡拉汉一起住了
So you're going to move in with Sam Callaghan.

546
00:43:33,640 --> 00:43:35,760
你以为这样会持久吗?
You think that will last?

547
00:43:38,880 --> 00:43:41,200
是的 我相信
I do, yes.

548
00:43:46,040 --> 00:43:48,280
- 对不起 - 够了
- I'm so sorry. - Enough.

549
00:43:48,400 --> 00:43:50,280
你走吧
Just go.

550
00:43:52,080 --> 00:43:55,720
我回家收拾一下东西
I'm going to have to pick up a few things from home.

551
00:43:55,840 --> 00:43:57,960
今晚不行
Not tonight.

552
00:43:59,040 --> 00:44:03,480
明天早上我会离开的 到时候你可以过来收拾
I'll make sure I'm gone tomorrow. You can pick them up then.

553
00:44:25,000 --> 00:44:26,440
# 任何人 #
Anyone

554
00:44:28,240 --> 00:44:31,920
# 你可以责怪我 #
You can blame me

555
00:44:32,040 --> 00:44:34,960
# 或者来羞辱我 #
Try to shame me

556
00:44:35,080 --> 00:44:39,640
# 我仍然在乎你 #
And still I'll care for you

557
00:44:43,880 --> 00:44:46,200
# 你可以四处游荡 #
You can run around

558
00:44:47,840 --> 00:44:50,480
# 甚至把我辜负 #
Even put me down

559
00:45:00,240 --> 00:45:05,240
# 世人也许笑我痴傻 #
The world may think I'm foolish

560
00:45:06,400 --> 00:45:10,480
# 他们无法看见 #
They can't see you

561
00:45:10,600 --> 00:45:13,520

# 我眼中的你 #
Like I can

562
00:45:13,640 --> 00:45:16,640
# 不过任何人 #
Oh, but anyone

563
00:45:18,160 --> 00:45:21,120
# 任何懂得爱的人 #
Who knows what love is

564
00:45:23,000 --> 00:45:26,920
# 终会明白 #
Will understand

565
00:45:35,000 --> 00:45:36,440
# 任何人 #
Anyone

566
00:45:39,040 --> 00:45:42,280
# 任何人 我只是为那些同情我的人#
Anyone I just feel so sorry

567
00:45:42,560 --> 00:45:47,560
# 任何人 觉得抱歉 #
Anyone For the ones who pity me...?
 

568
00:46:37,680 --> 00:46:39,760

辛普森夫人
Mrs Simpson.

569
00:46:39,920 --> 00:46:44,880
我想见山姆 不过他还没回来
I was supposed to meet Sam, but he hasn't come back yet.

570
00:46:45,040 --> 00:46:46,786
恐怕我帮不了你  
I'm afraid I can't help you. 

571
00:46:46,787 --> 00:46:48,920
拜托 他说他会在这里的
Please. He said he'd be here.

572
00:46:51,360 --> 00:46:53,400
稍等一下
Give me a moment.

573
00:47:12,520 --> 00:47:13,880
康!
Kang!

574
00:47:16,280 --> 00:47:18,080
郑夫人?
Mrs Cheng?

575
00:47:18,080 --> 00:47:19,580
我们找不到山姆

576
00:47:20,580 --> 00:47:21,580
他在这里吗?

577
00:47:21,880 --> 00:47:22,880
不在

578
00:47:26,580 --> 00:47:28,580
你知道他在哪里吗?

579
00:47:52,280 --> 00:47:55,400
你确定想看到这些吗?
Are you sure you want to see this?

580
00:48:12,840 --> 00:48:14,800
他... 他还好吗?
Is... is he alright?

581
00:48:14,920 --> 00:48:16,920
还好
Yeah.

582
00:48:17,080 --> 00:48:19,280
几个小时之内他哪里都不能去
He won't be going anywhere for a few hours.

583
00:48:19,440 --> 00:48:22,000
最好让他睡一会儿
Better to just let him sleep it off here.

584
00:48:22,160 --> 00:48:25,400
不用担心 我早上会带他回家的
Don't worry. I'll bring him home in the morning.

585
00:49:45,040 --> 00:49:47,160
我被录取了 哥伦比亚和乔治城
I got in. Columbia and Georgetown,

586
00:49:47,320 --> 00:49:50,440
纽约和华盛顿 被你说中了
New York and Washington DC, just like you said.

587
00:49:50,560 --> 00:49:52,440
太棒了
That's great.

588
00:49:54,000 --> 00:49:55,960
康拉德 怎么了?
Conrad, what's the matter?

589
00:49:58,720 --> 00:50:00,680
我销毁了你的文档
I destroyed your file.

590
00:50:00,800 --> 00:50:04,360
我跟你的朋友费利克斯聊了聊
I had a chat to your buddy Felix.

591
00:50:04,520 --> 00:50:06,560
我觉得他不会再找你麻烦了
I don't think that he'll bother you anymore.

592
00:50:06,720 --> 00:50:08,200
- 你做了什么? - 没什么
- What did you do? - Nothing.

593
00:50:08,320 --> 00:50:11,360
我们只是... 聊了聊
We just... had a little talk.

594
00:50:11,520 --> 00:50:15,080
但是从现在开始你必须低调行事
But I need you to stay under the radar from now on.

595
00:50:15,240 --> 00:50:17,800
- 康拉德 看 雷达呢 - 苏玲... 
- Conrad, look radar. - Su Ling...

596
00:50:17,920 --> 00:50:20,040
好吧 我什么也不干
OK. Yes, I'm not doing anything.

597
00:50:20,200 --> 00:50:24,480
不准聚会 不准跟你的朋友们谈论美国什么的
No rallies. No talking to your friends about the US or anything.

598
00:50:24,600 --> 00:50:25,960
都不准
Nothing.

599
00:50:27,360 --> 00:50:28,373
要多久?  
For how long? 

600
00:50:28,374 --> 00:50:30,400
只要你还想要签证就得这样
For as long as you want a visa.

601
00:50:30,520 --> 00:50:31,880
我把文件销毁了
I got rid of the file,

602
00:50:32,040 --> 00:50:34,080
但我不确定他们只有那一份材料
but I can't be certain that's the only one they have.

603
00:50:34,240 --> 00:50:37,240
要是他们发现你有这么一段前科还在制造麻烦
If they find out you've got a history and see you making trouble

604
00:50:37,400 --> 00:50:40,240
还跟人们谈论越南的事
and talking to people about Vietnam or anything,

605
00:50:40,400 --> 00:50:43,400
他们就会撤回你的签证并且把你遣回家
they will revoke your visa and they will send you home.

606
00:50:43,560 --> 00:50:45,480
- 不 他们不能这样 - 不 他们能
- No, they can't do that. - Yes, they can do that.

607
00:50:45,640 --> 00:50:49,040
因为有前科的人是不能得到学习签证的
Because people with histories don't get study visas.

608
00:50:49,160 --> 00:50:50,520
我要你向我保证
I need you to promise me

609
00:50:50,680 --> 00:50:55,160
从现在开始你会保持低调
that you will stay under the radar from now on.

610
00:50:55,280 --> 00:50:57,960
我保证 都听你的
I promise. Whatever you say.

611
00:50:58,080 --> 00:51:00,160
哈里森先生
Mr Harrison.

612
00:51:00,280 --> 00:51:02,760
我能跟你说两句吗?
Can we have a word?

613
00:51:02,880 --> 00:51:05,960
恐怕要单独谈谈
Alone, I'm afraid.

614
00:51:16,680 --> 00:51:18,520
女孩子很漂亮呢
Pretty girl.

615
00:51:23,800 --> 00:51:26,480
你想让我找到她的档案
You wanted me to find her file.

616
00:51:26,640 --> 00:51:28,400
所以你才给我们情报
That's why you gave us the intelligence.

617
00:51:28,560 --> 00:51:31,560
别担心 这些只有这么多了
Don't worry. These go no further than here.

618
00:51:33,080 --> 00:51:36,960
我们有很多有意思的照片
We have many interesting photographs.

619
00:52:06,040 --> 00:52:07,560
听说你搞丢了一些澳大利亚女孩
Heard you lost a couple of Australian girls.

620
00:52:07,720 --> 00:52:09,360
她们没上船
The girls weren't on the ship when it docked

621
00:52:09,520 --> 00:52:11,480
并且在新加坡乘客没有登陆记录
and Customs has no record of disembarkation in Singapore.

622
00:52:11,600 --> 00:52:13,280
要不他们会杀了她们
拢10,000 or they'll kill 'em.

623
00:52:13,440 --> 00:52:15,084
谁控制岸边这一带? 
Who controls the waterfront? 

624
00:52:15,085 --> 00:52:16,400
凯・索和他的团伙
Kay Song and his thugs.

625
00:52:16,560 --> 00:52:18,373
"格雷齐尔的女儿相当恐怖" 
'Grazier's Daughter Triad Horror.' 

626
00:52:18,374 --> 00:52:19,280
这故事里面说的
The story writes itself.

627
00:52:19,440 --> 00:52:21,680
你应该感激我没有即刻杀了你
You should be grateful I don't kill you where you stand.

628
00:52:23,480 --> 00:52:25,040
你是我和兰利的新纽带
You're my new conduit into Langley.

629
00:52:25,200 --> 00:52:27,600
你想让我为你监视中情局?
You want me to spy on the CIA for you?

630
00:52:27,760 --> 00:52:29,160
- 我看见你丈夫了 - 你看见?
- I saw your husband... - Did you see...?

631
00:52:29,320 --> 00:52:30,297
就在他死的那晚 
...on the night he died.

632
00:52:30,298 --> 00:52:31,520
你知道是怎么回事吗?
Do you know what happened?

633
00:52:31,640 --> 00:52:33,720
振作点 你现在是一名真正的间谍了
Chin up. You're a real spy now.

